===Relay (4 × 6 km)===
This event was first held in 1984. Through 1988, the event was 3 × 5&nbsp;km. 1989–91: 3 × 7.5&nbsp;km. 1993–2001: 4 × 7.5&nbsp;km. In 2003, the leg distance was set to 6&nbsp;km.
